BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 205.2 720 Td (Chapter 1: I Was Born) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Hello! I am Earth, your planet. Let me tell you my life story!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (I was born about 4.5 billion years ago from a swirling cloud of gas and dust.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (The Sun formed first, and leftover material clumped together to make the planets.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (At first, I was a ball of melting rock, constantly bombarded by asteroids!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (Slowly, I cooled down. Heavy metals sank to my center. Lighter rock floated up.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (Over millions of years, I formed my layers - like a giant rocky onion!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: HOW EARTH FORMED) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Our solar system formed from a giant cloud of gas and dust \(solar nebula\) 4.6 billion years ago.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Gravity pulled material together. The center became the Sun; leftovers became planets.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Earth formed from billions of rocky and metallic pieces smashing and sticking together.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Early Earth was so hot that the entire surface was molten \(liquid\) rock!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (As it cooled, heavier elements \(iron, nickel\) sank to the center forming the core.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Lighter rocks floated up to form the crust. Water appeared from volcanic gases and comets.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 374 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 433 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 413 Td (* Earth is 4.54 billion years old - if Earth's history were a 24-hour clock, humans appear at 11:59 PM!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 395 Td (* The Moon formed when a Mars-sized object crashed into young Earth, ejecting debris.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 377 Td (* Early Earth had no oxygen in its atmosphere - you could not have breathed the air!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 344 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 328 Td (Mix oil and water in a jar, shake, then watch them separate. Heavy stuff sinks - like Earth forming layers!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 308 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 292 Td (If Earth is 4.5 billion years old, how old is that compared to a human lifetime?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
