BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 181.2 720 Td (Chapter 4: My Fiery Breath) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (Sometimes my insides get so hot that melted rock pushes up through my skin!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (BOOM! A volcano erupts, shooting lava, ash, and gas high into the sky!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (I have about 1,500 active volcanoes around the world right now.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (Most of them are along the edges of my plates - a ring around the Pacific Ocean!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (Scientists call it the Ring of Fire because so many volcanoes circle the Pacific.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (My volcanoes helped create my atmosphere and even brought water to my surface!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: VOLCANOES) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Magma is melted rock below the surface; lava is melted rock ABOVE the surface.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Volcanoes form where magma finds a path up through cracks in the crust.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Shield volcanoes: wide and flat \(Hawaii\) - gentle lava flows.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Stratovolcanoes: tall and steep \(Mt. Fuji\) - explosive and dangerous.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (The Ring of Fire: 75% of the world's volcanoes circle the Pacific Ocean.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 464 Td (Volcanic eruptions helped form Earth's atmosphere by releasing gases from deep inside.) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 374 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 433 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 413 Td (* There are more volcanoes under the ocean than on land!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 395 Td (* The biggest volcano on Earth is Mauna Loa in Hawaii \(measured from the ocean floor\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 377 Td (* Volcanic soil is extremely fertile - that is why people live near volcanoes despite the danger.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 344 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 328 Td (Build a volcano: pile sand around a cup, add baking soda inside, pour vinegar + red food coloring. ERUPTION!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 308 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 292 Td (Why do people choose to live near active volcanoes despite the danger?) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
