BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 181.2 720 Td (Chapter 5: My Blue Blanket) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (I am wrapped in a beautiful invisible blanket called the atmosphere!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (It is made of gases: mostly nitrogen \(78%\) and oxygen \(21%\) that you breathe.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (My atmosphere protects you from the Sun's harmful rays and from space rocks!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (Without it, daytime would be boiling hot and nighttime would be freezing cold.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (It also keeps my temperature just right for life - like a greenhouse for the whole planet!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (But lately, humans are adding too many greenhouse gases and my blanket is getting too thick.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: THE ATMOSPHERE) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (The atmosphere has layers: troposphere \(weather\), stratosphere \(ozone\), mesosphere, thermosphere.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (The ozone layer \(in stratosphere\) blocks 97% of the Sun's harmful UV radiation.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Greenhouse effect: gases trap heat and keep Earth warm enough for life \(naturally good!\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (BUT: extra CO2 from burning fossil fuels makes the greenhouse effect too strong.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 480 Td (This 'enhanced' greenhouse effect is causing Earth's temperature to rise \(climate change\).) Tj ET
q 0.92 g 67 390 478 89 re f Q
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 77 449 Td (SCIENCE FACT BOX) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 429 Td (* 99% of the atmosphere is within 20 miles of the surface. Space is closer than you think!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 411 Td (* Without the greenhouse effect, Earth would average -18C \(0F\) instead of 15C \(59F\).) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 393 Td (* The atmosphere weighs 5.5 quadrillion tons - pressing on you with 14.7 lbs per square inch!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 360 Td (TRY THIS!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 10 Tf 82 344 Td (Put a thermometer in a sealed clear jar in the sun vs one outside. The jar heats up more = greenhouse effect!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 11 Tf 72 324 Td (THINK ABOUT IT:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F4 10 Tf 82 308 Td (What would Earth be like without an atmosphere? \(Hint: look at the Moon!\)) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
