BT 0 g /F2 20 Tf 147.6 720 Td (Chapter 8: Please Take Care of Me) Tj ET
q 0.5 G 1 w 72 710 m 540 710 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 680 Td (I have taken care of life for 4.5 billion years. Now I need YOUR help!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 664 Td (My climate is changing faster than at any time in millions of years.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 648 Td (My forests are shrinking. My oceans are warming. My ice caps are melting.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 632 Td (But here is the good news: humans are the smartest species I have ever hosted!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 616 Td (You have the knowledge to fix these problems if you work together.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 600 Td (Every small action matters - from recycling to planting trees to using less energy!) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F2 13 Tf 72 564 Td (THE SCIENCE: TAKING CARE OF EARTH) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 544 Td (Climate change: Earth's average temperature rising due to extra greenhouse gases.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 528 Td (Effects: melting ice, rising seas, more extreme weather, habitat loss.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 512 Td (Solutions: renewable energy, planting trees, reducing waste, sustainable living.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 72 496 Td (Conservation: protecting ecosystems, endangered species, and natural resources.) Tj ET
